Glade M. Knight: Executive Profile & Biography - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 23, 2017 1:45 AM ET
Real Estate Management and Development

Company Overview of Apple Suites Realty Group, Inc.



SnapshotPeople 




OverviewBoard MembersCommittees



Executive Profile
Glade M. Knight  Chairman and Chief Executive Officer, Apple Suites Realty Group, Inc.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 12 Board Members in 12 different organizations across 10 different industries.See Board Relationships73--
Background

		Mr. Glade M. Knight serves as Chairman of the Board and Chief Executive Officer of Energy Resources 12 GP, LLC. Mr. Knight has been Chairman and Chief Executive Officer at Energy 11 GP LLC, the General Partner of Energy 11, L.P. since its formation in July 2013 and its part owner. Mr. Knight serves as the Chairman and Chief Executive Officer at Apple Suites Realty Group, Inc., Apple REIT Ten, Inc and Apple Suites, Inc. He serves as Chairman, Chief Executive Officer and ... President of 5280 Lodging, LLC. Mr. Knight is Founder of Apple Hospitality REIT, Inc. and has been the Executive Chairman since May 15, 2014. He is also the Founder, Chairman and Chief Executive Officer at Apple REIT Seven Inc. and Apple REIT Eight Inc. He serves as Chief Executive Officer of Apple REIT Nine Inc. and Homewood Suites Charlotte Airport Hotel. He serves as Chairman and Chief Executive Officer of Apple REIT Companies. He was the Founder of Apple REIT Six, Inc.,. and served as its Chairman and Chief Executive Officer from 2004 until merged with an affiliate of Blackstone Real Estate Partners VII in May 2013. He served as President of Apple Hospitality Five Inc. until May 2007. He was Founder of BRE Select Hotels Corp. and served as its Chairman of the Board and Chief Executive Officer until May 13, 2013. Mr. Knight was the Chairman of the Board and Chief Executive Officer of Apple Hospitality Two, Inc., from 2001 to 2007 and Apple Hospitality Five, Inc., from 2002 to October of 2007. In addition, Mr. Knight served as Chairman and Chief Executive Officer of Cornerstone Realty Income Trust, Inc. since 1993 until 2005 and served as its President until October 13, 2003. From 2005 to April 2011, he served as a Trustee of Colonial Properties Trust of Colonial Realty Limited Partnership. He helped found and is the Chairman of Southern Virginia University, where he is the recipient of an Honorary Doctorate from that institution. He has been a Director of Apple Hospitality REIT, Inc. since 2007. He served as a Director of Apple Hospitality Two Inc from 2000 to 2007 and BRE Select Hotels Corp. since 2004. Mr. Knight served as a Director of Cornerstone Realty Income Trust Inc. since 1989. He is a Member of the Advisory Board of the Graduate School of Real Estate and Urban Land Development at Virginia Commonwealth University and a Member of the University’s Real Estate Circle of Excellence. Mr. Knight has served on a National Advisory Council for Brigham Young University and is a founding member of the University of the Graduate School of Business Management. He earned an M.B.A. in Finance from Marriott School of Management, Brigham Young University and Bachelor of Arts in Political Science from Brigham Young University.Read Full Background




