Insider Activity


Individual




Glade M. Knight



Mr. Glade M. Knight is Chairman & Chief Executive Officer at Apple REIT Ten, Inc., Chairman & Chief Executive Officer at Apple REIT Nine, Inc., Chairman & Chief Executive Officer at Apple REIT Eight, Inc., Chairman & Chief Executive Officer at Apple REIT Seven, Inc., Chairman & Chief Executive Officer at Apple Suites, Inc., Chairman at Southern Virginia University, Founding Member-Entrepreneurial Department at Brigham Young University, and Chairman & Chief Executive Officer at Apple REIT Cos., Inc. He founded Apple REIT Cos. in 1999.
Mr. Knight was previously employed as a Trustee by Colonial Properties Trust, Chairman & Chief Executive Officer by Apple REIT Six, Inc., Chairman & Chief Executive Officer by Apple Hospitality Two, Inc., Chairman & Chief Executive Officer by Cornerstone Realty Income Trust, Inc., a Trustee by Colonial Realty LP, and a Trustee by First Freedom Center.



